188: Intra uses a single weight (400) of one typeface (Whyte) at radically different sizes. The 95px display scale is not decoration — it replaces the role that color, iconography, and buttons play on a conventional site. When a new section needs emphasis, scale the type up, never add a color, never add a weight, never add a graphic. This is a constraint, not a limitation: it forces the content to be the visual hierarchy.
