190: | 2 | Ember Feature | `#fc5000` | Featured stat cards and emphasis surfaces — the only chromatic surface elevation |
191: | 3 | Plasma Hero | `#524ae9` | Hero halftone block — reserved for the homepage hero gradient overlay |
