264: - **Raycast** — Desktop-application metaphor extended to the web, with file-manager sidebars and window-like content areas
265: - **Vercel** — Tight tracking on geometric sans-serifs, hairline-border card system, and monochrome-with-single-accent color philosophy
266: - **Cal.com** — Warm sandy/beige background with small radii, flat surfaces, and a tactile 'printed' quality rather than glassmorphic
267: - **Cursor** — Developer-tool UI that frames the product as a desktop application with file-like content containers
